#GREP Usage

List out the filenames containing the string
grep -l "string"  /directiry_loction

display next 10 lines  after each stringmatch
grep -A 10 "string"  filename

display 4 line before each string appearence
grep -B 4 "string" fimename

take count of string match
grep -c "string"  filename

search the string in all files in the directory
grep -ir "srting" /directory
